In 1960, O5-4 descended to [[[scp-7600 |SCP-7600]]], known by its inhabitants as "Druv'tuul". In preparation for the possible interference that the city's ambient EVE radiation could have on cameras, he brought a series of small notebooks. In these, he sketched the many remarkable things he saw during his eventful visit. These are fragments of some of the pages in those notebooks: 

